                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190217-102-off598 t18190217-102-cd599"></join>, one apron, value 2 s.; two pair of scissars, value 2 s., and one pair of curling-irons, value 1 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18190217-102-victim947" type="victimName">
